106
00:10:10,333 --> 00:10:13,325
- Regarde-la.
- Qui est-ce?

107
00:10:13,413 --> 00:10:17,201
Je ne sais pas, c'est daté de 1775.

108
00:10:17,293 --> 00:10:20,205
