- ..Casper.

209
00:17:45,573 --> 00:17:49,532
Salut, Will! Tu as un très joli ''Boo!''.

210
00:17:52,933 --> 00:17:55,493
Tout le monde à l'intérieur.

211
00:17:59,773 --> 00:18:03,402
JOYEUX HALLOWEEN

212
